<HEADLINE>
VALENTINE'S TIMING MIGHT NEED WORK, IT SEEMS 
</HEADLINE>
  (Repeating to add photo note.) 
(With BBN-METS-DIAMONDBACKS) 
(ART ADV: Photos are being sent to NYT photo clients.
