603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(mk) 
 By JUDY BATTISTA   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Bobby Valentine was a championship ballroom dancer as
a teen-ager, but his sense of timing could not have been worse this
