<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPORTS-NYT-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
 Attn Sports Editors:  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Sports stories from The New York Times News Service for Sunday,
October 10, 1999.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BASEBALL PLAYOFFS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKEES-RANGERS (Arlington, Texas) _ Game 3 of the AL
Division Series: Yanks vs. Rangers at The Ballpark, 7:40 p.m. By
Buster Olney.
</P>
<P>
   With sidebars as warranted.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-METS-DIAMONDBACKS (New York) _ Game 4 of the NL Division
