<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-09 12:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5123 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-POLITICS-SEX-REVIEW-2     10-09 1131
