<P>
   GORE-BRADLEY _ DES MOINES _ Vice President Gore and former New
Jersey senator Bill Bradley appear together Saturday night at the
Iowa Democratic Party's big, annual fund-raiser. The meeting will
be their first since Gore shifted his campaign operation to
Tennessee and vowed to fight Bradley for the nomination as though
he were the underdog. (Foskett, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
