<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-09 16:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1852 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-BBN-ANDERSON-COLUMN-1     10-09 0849
